        <item>
            <title>值得为 Monster Hunter Wild 买 PS5 Pro 吗？，直接比较 PS5 Pro、PS5 表现</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/monster-hunter-wild-worth-ps5-pro/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=monster-hunter-wild-worth-ps5-pro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/monster-hunter-wild-worth-ps5-pro/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 12:38:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Monster Hunter Wild]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[playstation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PlayStation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY PlayStation 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1289683</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》今日正式推出 PS5 试玩版，无论你是久经沙场的资深猎人，还是初踏狩猎之旅的新手，相信都在犹豫是否值得为《Monster Hunter Wild》添置或升级 PS5 Pro。为了让大家了解两者的表现差异，小编特意录制了同一场景下，分别使用 PS5 及 PS5 Pro 游玩《Monster Hunter Wilds》的实机片段，让大家观看后再衡量是否购入或升级至 PS5 Pro，以享受更流畅的狩猎体验。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atthlg_6bp024ntyamhd-524x580.jpg" alt="" width="524" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atthlg_6bp024ntyamhd-524x580.jpg 524w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atthlg_6bp024ntyamhd.jpg 813w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 524px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/obt2_thumb_jajp-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/obt2_thumb_jajp-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/obt2_thumb_jajp.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>目前官方尚未正式加入「PS5 Pro Enhanced」功能，预计将于正式版推出时同步加入。因此本次测试不会针对 PS5 Pro 与 PS5 之间的画质差异进行评价，而是专注于流畅度与游戏体验。先说结论：</p><p>如果你对 FPS 下降或「窒画面」较为敏感，且希望享受更稳定的狩猎体验，那么升级至 PS5 Pro 无疑是更值得考虑的选择。以下是我们在 PS5 与 PS5 Pro 上实测的几个关键场景，让大家可以更直观地比较两者的表现。游戏设定为「画质模式」，所有影片均以 PS5 内置萤幕录制功能拍摄，确保对比公平。</p><h3><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/attua_scnalxrdo4vqvw-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/attua_scnalxrdo4vqvw-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/attua_scnalxrdo4vqvw.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atttlf8z9zskbpmq8sq4-1-694x367.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atttlf8z9zskbpmq8sq4-1-694x367.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/atttlf8z9zskbpmq8sq4-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>因为官方尚未加入「PS5 Pro enhanced」功能，据悉会与正式版同步推出，故此评论 PS5 Pro 与 PS5 画面细致度表现，可说是言之尚早。但先讲讲结论，小编觉得如果你无法容忍低 FPS、跌格问题的话，非常值得为「芒亨」购买／升级 PS5 Pro。下面小编会分享数段分别使用 PS5 Pro 和 PS5 在同一场景游玩的片段供大家参考。全部影片均以 PS5 机内萤幕录制功能拍摄。</p><h2>日光表现</h2><h2>PS5 Pro</h2><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="值得为 Monster Hunter Wild 买 PS5 Pro 吗？，PS5 Pro-6 日间表现" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1054466483?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>
PS5 Pro</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="值得为 Monster Hunter Wild 买 PS5 Pro 吗？，PS5 Pro-4 战斗体验" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1054449635?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><h2><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
PS5</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="值得为 Monster Hunter Wild 买 PS5 Pro 吗？，PS5-4 战斗体验" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1054449645?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>玩芒亨时与魔物对战时的操控手感非常关键，甚至能影响整体狩猎的流畅度与精准度。小编与同事轮流使用 PS5 Pro 进行测试，发现更高的 FPS 除了视觉上更加顺畅更赏心悦目，更直接影响战斗中即时反应与操作精确度。PS5 Pro 版本画面流畅度显著提升，使得玩家能更精确地掌握攻击时机。例如在锁定魔物的弱点／伤口连续攻击时，PS5 Pro 画面与操作更加同步，每一次出招都能准确命中，而不会因为「跌格」而错失最佳攻击时机。相较之下，PS5 在 FPS 稍有波动时，出招连续感会略显生硬，玩家需更高适应性来调整攻击节奏。</p></div></div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
